SELECT CASE 
 WHEN (SELECT Count(*) 
 FROM store_sales 
 WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20) > 3672 THEN 
 (SELECT Avg(ss_ext_list_price) 
 FROM store_sales 
 WHERE 
 ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20) 
 ELSE (SELECT Avg(ss_net_profit) 
 FROM store_sales 
 WHERE ss_quantity BETWEEN 1 AND 20) 
 END bucket1,
